{
  "title": "Xtra Smoky Slovakian Pork Skewers",
  "description": "Tangy and pillowy Slovakian dish featuring mustard and mirepoix base, perfect for midnight cravings, grilled to perfection on a robata grill.",
  "cuisine": "Slovakian",
